translation[10]{c,v,t}:
  24,1,(Esi) sisahluko se’Kur’ân eSisithumele phantsi Saza Senza (okuphakathi kuso) kwaba sisinyanzelo Saza kananjalo Satyhila phakathi apho iiVesi eziyimiqondiso ecacileyo ukuze nikhumbule
  24,2,"Owasetyhini (ongatshatanga) okanye oyindoda (ongatshanga). Ofunyenwe enetyala lokwabelana ngesondo, mtywatyusheni ngamnye kubo bobabini imivumbo elikhulu, kananjalo ningathatyathwa lusizi ngabo enkolweni ka- Allâh ukuba ngaba phofu niyakholwa kuAllâh nakwiMini yokuGqibela. Kananjalo makubekho iqela lamakholwa aza kuba ngamangqina ngesohlwayo sabo"
  24,3,"Umkrexezi akamtshati (omnye umntu) ngaphandle kongumkrexezikazi okanye umkhonzikazi wezithixo, kanti (naye) umkrexezikazi akatshatwa mntu ngaphandle komkrexezi okanye umkhonzi wezithixo. Ke kaloku (ukutshata abanjalo) akuvumelekanga kwabakholwayo"
  24,4,Abo batyhola abafazi abanyulu (ngokukrexeza bexoka) baze bangezi namangqina amane batywatyusheni ngemivumbo engamashumi asibhozo ningaphindi namkele bungqina kubo nanini na emva koko. Yaye abo ngabaqaqadeki abangenantobeko
  24,5,"Ngaphandle kwabo baguqukayo emva koko baze baphucule isimilo sabo, kuba ngenene, uAllâh nguMxoleli, nguSozinceba"
  24,6,"Abo batyhola abafazi babo (ngokukrexeza) babe bengenamangqina ngaphandle kweziqu zabo ke kaloku ingqina lakhe ngamnye kubo (iya kuba) kukungqina kane (befunga) ngoAllâh okokuba, ngenene, yena lowo (ufungayo) ungothetha inyaniso"
  24,7,Isifungo sesihlanu sona (iya kuba) kukuba isiqalekiso sika-Allâh sibe phezu kwakhe ukuba ngaba ufumaniseke engomnye wamaxoki
  24,8,Kodwa ke oko kuya kuthintela isohlwayo kuye (owasetyhini) ukuba uthe wanika ubungqina kwaba kane (efunga) ngoAllâh ukuba ngenene yena (oyindoda yakhe) ungothetha ubuxoki
  24,9,Esesihlanu (isifungo) iya kuba kukuba ingqumbo ka-Allâh ibe phezu kwakhe (umfazi lowo) ukuba yena (oyindoda) uthetha inyaniso
  24,10,"Ukuba bekungekho ngenxa yobabalo luka-Allâh kuni nenceba yaKhe (UAllâh Ebeza kungxama ukuthoba isohlwayo phezu kwenu kodwa ke akunjalo) kuba kakade (eneneni) uAllâh UnguMamkeli, wenguquko nguSobulumko"